<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <title>Your Startup - Welcome to Success</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="styles.css">
</head>

<body>
  <header>
    <nav>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
        <li><a href="#services">Services</a></li>
        <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <section id="hero">
    <h1>Welcome to Your Startup</h1>
    <p>Transforming Ideas into Reality</p>
    <a href="#contact" class="btn">Get Started</a>
  </section>

  <section id="about">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>About Us</h2>
      <p>Your Startup is a forward-thinking company focused on innovation and problem-solving. We believe that every idea has the potential to change the world, and we are here to turn those ideas into successful ventures.</p>
      <p>With a team of dedicated experts and a passion for excellence, we provide comprehensive solutions tailored to the needs of startups and entrepreneurs.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="services">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Our Services</h2>
      <div class="service">
        <img src="service1.jpg" alt="Service 1">
        <h3>Idea Validation</h3>
        <p>We help you validate your business idea through market research, competitor analysis, and feasibility studies.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="service">
        <img src="service2.jpg" alt="Service 2">
        <h3>Product Development</h3>
        <p>Our expert team assists you in developing a scalable product or service that meets market demands and delights customers.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="service">
        <img src="service3.jpg" alt="Service 3">
        <h3>Marketing Strategy</h3>
        <p>We craft effective marketing strategies to help your startup reach and engage with the right audience.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="contact">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <form>
        <input type="text" placeholder="Name" required>
        <input type="email" placeholder="Email" required>
        <textarea placeholder="Message" required></textarea>
        <button type="submit">Send</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2023 Your Startup. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>

</body>

</html>
